        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6178ffb5-4c35-465e-afbd-9ad36b17b25c">
                Mr. Stanley
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6178ffb5-4c35-465e-afbd-9ad36b17b25c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-04-05/debates/5f925cfd-9737-4257-a64f-a4e841deb8fe/WarRisksInsurance#contribution-6178ffb5-4c35-465e-afbd-9ad36b17b25c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As I indicated in the answer I gave on 1st February to the hon. Member for Tamworth (Sir J. Mellor), this matter is receiving consideration, but I am not at present able to make any further statement.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6178ffb5-4c35-465e-afbd-9ad36b17b25c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
